        DIDN_T_THINK_I_D_EVER_HEAR_THOSE                                     = 7478,  -- %? Didn't think I'd ever hear those words from someone who wasn't a Gob. You know some weird stuff, for a person.
        THERE_S_A_STORY_THAT_SAYS_SOME_THINGS                                = 7479,  -- There's a story that says some things have their own soul.
        THE_USED_TO_BE_JUST_SIMPLE_HOURGLASSES_BUT                           = 7480,  -- The % used to be just simple hourglasses. But as they passed through the hands of dozens of people, and even a few beastmen as well, the hourglasses were transformed by all their thoughts and feelings.
        THEY_HAVE_THE_ABILITY_TO_FOCUS_MYSTERIOUS_POWERS                     = 7481,  -- They have the ability to focus mysterious powers. In our travels through all the lands of this world, us Goblins often come across this sorta thing.
        NOW_WE_COME_TO_THE_FUN_PART_IF                                       = 7482,  -- Now we come to the fun part. If you want a %, I'd be willing to sell one to you. And you should know that only us Gobs can tell if an item has its own soul.
