        DID_YA_KNOW_THAT_SOME_ITEMS_HAVE_THEIR                               = 7491,  -- Did ya know that some items have their own soul? After passing through the hands of hundreds of people, not to mention the paws of us beastmen, some items are transformed through contact with all those thoughts and feelings.
        THESE_TRANSFORMED_ITEMS_HAVE_THE_ABILITY_TO_FOCUS                    = 7492,  -- These transformed items have the ability to focus mysterious powers. Us Goblins often come across this weird phenenom...phemomeno...stuff in our travels.
        YA_KNOW_IF_YA_REALLY_WANT_I_COULD                                    = 7493,  -- Ya know, if ya really want %, I could sell one to ya for the right price.
        BUT_LET_ME_TELL_YA_KID_ONLY_US                                       = 7494,  -- But let me tell ya, kid. Only us Gobs can tell if an item is souled. Not even other beastmen--and definitely not you people--can tell the difference between normal junk and priceless artifacts.
