        THIS_ONE_S_THE_LEAST_VALUABLE_OF_THE                                 = 7512,  -- This one's the least valuable of the lot. It was used as a part of the San d'Orian currency years ago. I know I told ya about the nations all having different currencies, but these San d'Orian coins are the only ones I'm interested in.
