        NOW_THIS_IS_THE_GOOD_PART_THE_WEAPONS                                = 7639,  -- Now, this is the good part. The weapons those guys found happen to have the same sorta aura as the % you're toting around. Pretty intriguing stuff, wouldn't you say?
